Title: Mushan Mastery
Description:
Mushan! Would ya look at the size o' 'em. Old as the dirt they walk on probably. A fine trophy.

If you are lookin' to test your mettle as a big game hunter, start with them.
CompletionText: They didn't send ya' runin' did they?
RewardText:
Well done $p.

My father travels across the sea to a new continent and all he can seem ta' want to hunt is old borin' wolves.

Me, I like to hunt stuff with meat on its bones.
